headline: NTRS Q4 Deep Dive: Wealth Management and AI Productivity Drive Outperformance
summary: Financial services company Northern Trust (NASDAQ:NTRS) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 8.2% year on year to $2.13 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.42 per share was 2% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
